articles.title: Australia's Qantas to close budget airline Jetstar Asia - BBC
articles.description: Jetstar Asia has struggled with rising supplier costs, high airport fees and increased competition.
articles.content:
Singapore-based budget airline Jetstar Asia will close down at the end of July, with more than 500 employees laid-off.
